{"type": "article", "id": 17593, "title": "海藻圆凳", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-16T07:10:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000358UDwjQrz2IWfhP73k.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师往往擅长发掘材料的无限可能，德国设计师 Carolin Pertsch 带来的这组高脚凳就用了海藻。为了保持海岸的干净，每年都有数千吨海藻被清理掉。她从德国的海边采集了大叶藻，结合生物树脂做了凳子的座位，坐上去感觉像软木。除了创造一种生态材料，她还想要提醒人们开拓眼界，思考未来可能改变生活的新材料。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144643vAOip48kI5dGCDja.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"772\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144644QNInXwdm9PhLRJHT.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144645FqkAtOY6e2saXmg5.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://cms.qdaily.com/uploads/image/201511/9c2a4ac4ba7f.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"517\" title=\" \" alt=\" \">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}